text: Cleisostoma sagittatum is a species of orchid found in Borneo, Java, the Philippines and Sumatra.Cleisostoma sagittatum This species was first described by Blume in 1825. == References == == External links == sagittatum Category:Orchids of the Philippines Category:Orchids of Sumatra Category:Orchids of Java Category:Orchids of Borneo
